<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
      .user-info { background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>âœ… Login Details Sent</h1>
        <p>Confirmation Notification</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>Hi Jamie,</strong></p>
        
        <p>This is to confirm that login credentials have been successfully sent to:</p>

        <div class="user-info">
          <p><strong>User:</strong> <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
          <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= @temp_password %></p>
          <p><strong>Sent at:</strong> <%= Time.current.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>The user should now be able to log in to their Bravik account.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated confirmation from the Bravik admin system.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>